      • getCommand

        public ValidCommand getCommand(String label)
        Gets the custom command of the given name. This can be either the command's name or one of it's aliases. Will return null if no match was found, which should never happen assuming the command registration went properly.
        Parameters:
        label - the label of the command.
        Returns:
        the command, if one exists.
